02:10:10,376 --> 02:10:11,216
Could you please stand?

575
02:10:22,168 --> 02:10:35,635
30 years, Adeline Laney Cahill, Michael Coates, Robert Ferrante, Debra Notaro, Diane Serbanian, Lynn Travers, Lauren McCarthy.

576
02:10:35,655 --> 02:10:48,642
40 years of service, Marie Cunningham and Anne Patton.

