579
02:12:24,953 --> 02:12:38,395
Medford Public Schools and Tufts University honor Marie Cassidy, founder of the Medford Family Network, Dr. Suzanne Begalusi, superintendent, and Mr. Rocco DiRico, associate vice president of government and community relations at Tufts University.

580
02:12:39,996 --> 02:12:40,536
Thank you.

581
02:12:45,997 --> 02:12:49,098
I'm just going to say a little brief, if that's OK, Mr. DiRico.

582
02:12:51,298 --> 02:13:02,565
I mean, where do we begin to talk about Marie Cassidy and the impact she's made on the Medford community since 1993?

583
02:13:03,225 --> 02:13:10,250
So it's impossible to sum up into words what Marie Cassidy means to the city of Medford and to Medford families.

584
02:13:11,372 --> 02:13:12,473
we could try.

585
02:13:13,434 --> 02:13:17,117
She's been the driving force to the Medford Family Network.

586
02:13:17,837 --> 02:13:37,753
She started the program and has just with persistence, grit, love, and dedication has just poured her entire self into the program as well as the Medford community and for that many Medford families have felt that support

587
02:13:38,292 --> 02:13:47,877
through the resources, the guidance, the training, and the materials that you've been able to provide to families for decades.

588
02:13:48,637 --> 02:13:53,960
So I know that we're not going to necessarily say goodbye to Marie.

589
02:13:53,980 --> 02:13:55,861
I don't think that that's possible.

590
02:13:56,481 --> 02:14:03,185
But I do want to, on behalf of Medford Public Schools, thank you for everything you've done for our families and for our students.

591
02:14:03,665 --> 02:14:07,247
Your impact is profound, and it is seen, visible, and felt.

592
02:14:08,107 --> 02:14:08,648
So thank you.

593
02:14:10,469 --> 02:14:14,732
Thank you Mayor Lungo-Kern, Dr. Galluzzi, and the members of the Medford School Committee.

594
02:14:15,272 --> 02:14:16,273
My name is Rocco DiRico.

595
02:14:16,333 --> 02:14:19,916
I'm the Associate Vice President of Government Community Relations at Tufts University.

596
02:14:21,097 --> 02:14:31,824
At Tufts, we often talk about the importance of civic engagement and we value our partnerships and collaborations with the city, Medford public schools, and local nonprofit organizations.

597
02:14:32,505 --> 02:14:35,627
We treasure our partnership with the Medford Family Network.

598
02:14:36,427 --> 02:14:45,815
And as Dr. Galluzzi was saying, for over three decades, that iconic purple door has been a beacon for everyone in the community.

599
02:14:47,016 --> 02:14:57,444
And for so many families, over 400 Tufts families call Medford home, and many of those families have benefited from the programs at the Medford Family Network, including my own.

600
02:14:59,481 --> 02:15:03,808
And when we think about the heart and soul of the network, we think of Marie Cassidy.

601
02:15:04,929 --> 02:15:10,097
She is a fixture at the Medford Family Network, but she's also been a fixture at Tufts University.

602
02:15:10,638 --> 02:15:12,320
She's at Tufts Community Day every year.

603
02:15:12,340 --> 02:15:15,585
She has served on our Tisch College Community Research Board.

604
02:15:16,065 --> 02:15:21,068
She is an alumni, technically, because she received an honorary degree from Tufts as well.

605
02:15:22,309 --> 02:15:34,075
So today, on behalf of President Sunil Kumar and Tufts University, and in honor of Marie Cassidy, Tufts University would like to announce a $50,000 donation to the Medford Family Network.

606
02:15:41,960 --> 02:15:44,162
Oh my God, this is absolutely incredible.

607
02:15:44,242 --> 02:15:45,403
How do I begin?

608
02:15:45,503 --> 02:15:46,684
How do I say anything?

609
02:15:47,344 --> 02:15:49,186
You know, I'm just out to song, you know that.

610
02:15:51,227 --> 02:15:54,510
Good evening, school committee and everyone, how are you?

611
02:15:55,030 --> 02:15:56,011
Great, great.

612
02:15:56,551 --> 02:15:59,534
Good evening, school committee and everyone, how are you?

613
02:15:59,554 --> 02:16:00,434
Great, great.

614
02:16:01,952 --> 02:16:05,095
We all are here tonight because I think we got it right.

615
02:16:05,975 --> 02:16:08,838
Good evening school committee and everyone.

616
02:16:09,118 --> 02:16:09,719
How are you?

617
02:16:10,459 --> 02:16:11,460
Great, great.

618
02:16:12,381 --> 02:16:15,684
Thank you so, so much.

619
02:16:15,724 --> 02:16:17,025
I do not know where to begin.

620
02:16:17,045 --> 02:16:18,186
This is unbelievable.

621
02:16:18,626 --> 02:16:22,409
It has been more than a joy and an honor for me to have this role.

622
02:16:22,849 --> 02:16:25,732
I have been privileged every single day of my life.

623
02:16:25,812 --> 02:16:26,412
I really have.

624
02:16:26,753 --> 02:16:27,994
The good, the bad, and the ugly.

625
02:16:28,094 --> 02:16:29,014
Every moment of it.

626
02:16:29,755 --> 02:16:33,598
I look to our families and the star of this story is the story.

627
02:16:35,059 --> 02:16:50,313
the story of our families, of our members, of our struggles, of their struggles, and the winning of those struggles, and the getting through it, and the picking themselves up year after year, because we have an amazing staff, three of whom are here with me this evening.

628
02:16:51,033 --> 02:16:52,775
If you could please raise your wonderful hands.

629
02:16:53,015 --> 02:16:58,440
Irina Shumway is here, Brenda Kennedy is here, and Cindy Selbig.

630
02:16:58,920 --> 02:17:00,402
I have an amazing team.

631
02:17:02,435 --> 02:17:04,917
And they represent with me decades of work.

632
02:17:04,957 --> 02:17:09,560
I think we have like thousands of years of staff time when you pull it all together.

633
02:17:09,580 --> 02:17:11,662
It's been an amazing, amazing time.

634
02:17:12,382 --> 02:17:19,888
And this Medford School Committee and the Medford Public Schools have been opened up with welcome arms to us year after year.

635
02:17:20,168 --> 02:17:27,033
When we didn't have a place to be, all the schools, the elementary schools, of which there were 11 by the time, at that time if you may remember,

636
02:17:27,573 --> 02:17:31,634
opened up their arms to us and let the Medford Family Network have a place there.

637
02:17:32,095 --> 02:17:42,138
And then we opened up our arms at Medford High School in 2003 and we're able to be a really permanent place in the school, in the city.

638
02:17:42,158 --> 02:17:48,320
I don't know how to thank all of you enough to thank the city enough.

639
02:17:48,620 --> 02:17:52,001
Every organization, every business has opened up their arms to us.

640
02:17:52,421 --> 02:17:57,023
Tufts University, what an honor it has been to be with you and all of your students.

641
02:17:57,523 --> 02:18:06,446
I had taught scholars for many, many years, and they were amazing, and implemented programs that live to this day at the Medford Family Network.

642
02:18:07,426 --> 02:18:10,727
The focus group helped us set up every September.

643
02:18:11,148 --> 02:18:18,150
