The district has been doing a lot of planning and have engaged in a lot of conversation in the planning for next year.

783
02:30:20,189 --> 02:30:23,912
We're actually dedicating some of our administrative retreat to that, but we're trying to

784
02:30:24,352 --> 02:30:31,158
be proactive and make sure that some of the oversight that happened this year does not happen again.

