Ryan.

1168
03:11:20,303 --> 03:11:28,607
So does that mean teachers can or cannot use AI to create lessons?

1169
03:11:36,970 --> 03:11:37,470
Member Reinfeld?

1170
03:11:39,694 --> 03:11:44,418
Those guidelines outline how teachers can use in lesson planning, preparing assessments.

1171
03:11:44,978 --> 03:11:46,179
The guidelines go through that.

1172
03:11:46,399 --> 03:11:50,122
It is just the grading that I want, that needs to change.

1173
03:11:51,263 --> 03:11:55,846
So the teachers can use AI just in a certain way, right?

1174
03:11:57,027 --> 03:11:57,267
Yes.

1175
03:11:57,287 --> 03:11:57,748
